text: Dylan Hondo (born 28 May 1995) is a Zimbabwean cricketer. He is a left-handed batsman and a left-arm orthodox bowler. He made his first class debut against SL Dev EM XI He made his List A debut on 14 February 2020, for Rangers in the 2019–20 Pro50 Championship. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Zimbabwean cricketers Category:Rangers cricketers
